{"tid":2074200,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"工程巴下周二高院保釋覆核 跪求手足聲援","createTime":"2020-06-22T02:34:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T23:47:42.000Z","uid":57073,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"97fac450ade4be6edc9ab0c40dcbda4837f0e745","tid":2074200,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T02:34:29.000Z","msg":"工程巴下周二高院保釋覆核 跪求手足聲援<br />\n<br />\n實用工程admin（工程巴 ）將於 6月23日 早上9:30 於高等法院進行保釋覆核，跪求大家到場聲援。<br />\n<br />\n工程巴之後就要面對最高刑罰終身監禁的指控。無論結果如何，佢都希望大家從未忘記佢，可以陪佢面對。<br />\n<br />\n*親友委託<br />\n*請先讓位比親友入庭<br />\n*同日同庭會有被判重囚一年社工劉手足進行保釋上訴 請也要聲援劉手足"},{"pid":"5a3ae3338e8cd781516a0956223a35a9502c95cd","tid":2074200,"uid":162441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T09:38:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"56522c96e85c4fc64e52a7ebf2709ee93245e5be","tid":2074200,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T09:39:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"01304601d0cfbd77b3dbf902ef715bcc3f894743","tid":2074200,"uid":36044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T21:23:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"417b035f536e751ec09009541d411c2a724414f4","tid":2074200,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T21:24:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f14d1598208c3c4298b9a37a8f1aec0b3b4769df","tid":2074200,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T21:27:49.000Z","msg":"唔好推啦，睇三峽新聞仲好過啦"},{"pid":"f0144009a2cae4b4d47acfd0dc9d6b4ed511f112","tid":2074200,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T21:28:05.000Z","msg":"<img 